<p><strong>Last updated:</strong> April 3, 2026</p>

<h2>The short version</h2>
<p>We don't collect your data. No accounts, no cookies, no analytics trackers, no ads. Your game progress is saved locally in your browser using localStorage. We never see it.</p>

<h2>What we store</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Game saves:</strong> Stored in your browser's localStorage under keys starting with <code>ca-save-</code>. Never sent to any server.</li>
  <li><strong>Favorites and recently played:</strong> Stored in your browser's localStorage under <code>ca-favorites</code> and <code>ca-recent</code>. Never sent to any server.</li>
  <li><strong>Theme preference:</strong> Stored in your browser's localStorage under <code>theme</code>. Light or dark — that's it.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Multiplayer</h2>
<p>If you use the multiplayer feature, game data is transmitted directly between you and other players via WebRTC (peer-to-peer). No game data passes through our servers. Room codes are used only for peer discovery via public relay infrastructure (Nostr relays) and are not logged.</p>

<h2>Third-party services</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Cloudflare Pages:</strong> Hosts this website. Cloudflare may collect minimal server logs (IP address, request time) as part of standard web hosting. See <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cloudflare's privacy policy</a>.</li>
  <li><strong>Bunny Fonts:</strong> Serves web fonts. GDPR-compliant and privacy-focused. See <a href="https://bunny.net/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bunny.net's privacy policy</a>.</li>
  <li><strong>GTranslate:</strong> Provides page translation. See <a href="https://gtranslate.io/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GTranslate's privacy policy</a>.</li>
</ul>

<h2>No ads, no tracking</h2>
<p>This site contains no advertising, no tracking pixels, no analytics scripts, and no social media trackers. We believe you should be able to play games without being surveilled.</p>

<h2>Children's privacy</h2>
<p>We do not knowingly collect any personal information from anyone, including children. Since we collect no data, there is nothing to protect or delete.</p>

<h2>Clearing your data</h2>
<p>To remove all locally stored data, clear your browser's localStorage for this site. In most browsers: Developer Tools &rarr; Application &rarr; Local Storage &rarr; delete entries for this domain.</p>

<h2>Contact</h2>
<p>Questions about this policy? Reach us through <a href="https://www.pikespeakwebdesigns.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pikes Peak Web Designs</a>.</p>
